buried a 19yearold man gunned down on a sidewalk by gang members 
on good friday neither the dead man nor the 12 others injured in 
the bloody attack were gang members according to police and 
relatives 
this tragedy that has taken place we should see that it 
doesnt happen again by learning to love one another said the 
rev lea gibson 
