occasional party designed to show the house off to prospective 
buyers 
the mansion on 15 acres in the prestigious preston hollow area 
is believed to be the largest most expensive ever built on 
speculation in dallas it was completed last month but still does 
not have an owner 
but builder john needham who began the house more than two 
years ago when the citys housing economy was near its peak says 
he believes there is a market for his sevenbedroom creation 
there is an intense amount of interest in it but its 
hard to say with a house of this magnitude needham said 
the house does have magnitude 
needham was interviewed at a recent landscape lighting party 
